3 will it be clear_skies in the next two_days ?	the next two_days will be clear_skies , one will be clear_skies with a low of 70f and a high of 80f and the other will be foggy , low of 90f with a high of 100f
4 thanks	not a problem

3 for the whole week , please !	the weather this week for los_angeles is going to be a series of ups and downs from foggy on friday to a rain on tuesday and to blizzard on sunday the highs are forecast to be near 100f with lows near 20f
4 thank you so much for the information	you are welcome have a good day
